<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id60090d9d-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s661"><num value="661">§ 661.</num><heading> Short title; definitions</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id60090d9e-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s661/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> This chapter may be cited as the “Coal Research and Development Act of 1960”.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id60090d9f-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s661/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><chapeau> In this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id60090da0-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s661/b/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “research” means scientific, technical, and economic research and the practical application of that research.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id60090da1-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s661/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of Energy.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id60090da2-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/599/s1">Pub. L. 86–599, § 1</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tX/s1009/a/1/A">Pub. L. 109–58, title X, § 1009(a)(1)(A)</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/934">119 Stat. 934</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id60090da3-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">
