<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id60090da5-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 661, <ref href="/us/pl/86/599/s1">Pub. L. 86–599, § 1</ref>, <date date="1960-07-07">July 7, 1960</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/74/336">74 Stat. 336</ref>, defined terms for purposes of this chapter, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tX/s1009/a/1/A">Pub. L. 109–58, title X, § 1009(a)(1)(A)</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/934">119 Stat. 934</ref>.</p>
</note>
